column5: Fished for 20 minutes,no bites but had one doggy follow.  ..........HELP!!! I gotta fish soon  :D
Did you try flippin next to that wheel barrel?
Yup, I'm with Shore Lunch on that one. It'd be nice to hit the water together this coming season, Larry.
This photo would make a great photo for one of those photo caption contests...
It has been a long winter hasn't it?
Trade the dog in for an auger...
